### [Leviticus Chapter 19](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#001.md)

[Leviticus](../../../bib/kjv/lev001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">lev 19:0</span></span>

Exhortations to holiness, and a repetition of various laws, [Lev
19:1](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#001.md), [Lev
19:2](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#002.md) Duty to parents, and observance
of the Sabbath, [Lev 19:3](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#003.md). Against
idolatry, [Lev 19:4](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#004.md). Concerning
peace-offerings, [Lev 19:5-8](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#005.md). The
gleanings of the harvest and vintage to be left for the poor, [Lev
19:9](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#009.md), [Lev
19:10](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#010.md). Against stealing and lying,
[Lev 19:11](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#011.md); false swearing, [Lev
19:12](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#012.md); defrauding the hireling, [Lev
19:13](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#013.md). Laws in behalf of the deaf and
the blind, [Lev 19:14](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#014.md). Against respect
of persons in judgment, [Lev 19:15](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#015.md);
tale-bearing, [Lev 19:16](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#016.md); hatred and
uncharitableness, [Lev 19:17](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#017.md); revenge,
[Lev 19:18](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#018.md); unlawful mixtures in
