years, [Lev 19:23](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#023.md); but this is lawful
in the fourth and fifth years, [Lev
19:24](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#024.md), [Lev
19:25](../../../bib/kjv/lev019.htm#025.md). Against eating of blood, and
